data.description: Supremely situated above the iconic Kootenai River, this gorgeous Caribou Creek log home showcases mountain views, meticulous construction, and hand-crafted custom finishes. The river drifts below this exceptional vantage point where the trees frame the extended stretch of water, the valleys, and Yaak Mountain to the northeast. A short drive to town yet a world away as the private tree-lined drive escorts you to your peaceful and secluded mountain retreat. The bright interior embraces the views with plenty of space including a bedroom and bathroom on the main, spacious 600 sq.ft. loft en suite, and a partially finished full basement ready to customize your needs.  Step right into the lifestyle with a finished garden spot, indoor root cellar, wood shed, large 36X36 shop with bathroom, RV spot, and beautiful spaces to relax and take it all in at the end of a rewarding day. Step out your front door tohundreds of Stimson acres bordering this property. Adjacent land listed MLS#30013988 Call Josie Hermes, 208-640-3252, or your real estate professional.
